00:01:29.740 --> 00:01:34.790
important to me that we focus on areas that
impact that number. So, we've done everything

00:01:34.790 --> 00:01:38.800
we can with insulation, windows and doors.
And when it comes to the heating and cooling

00:01:38.800 --> 00:01:44.890
system, we're doing these mini-splits. And
that allows us to really cut the cost of our

00:01:44.890 --> 00:01:51.550
energy consumption by up to twenty-five percent.
So let's say the average cost for your utilities

00:01:51.550 --> 00:02:00.280
